items.name: Financial-Tracker-Expense-Tracker
items.description: Program that helps you to keep track of spending and budget efficiently. Allows you to categorize spending and uses weekly/monthly reports as well as charts to provide a detailed description of your spending habits in relation to your budget.

items.name: LLM-pdf-extraction
items.description: This project provides an API for uploading PDF documents and extracting structured summaries using either OpenAI's GPT-4o or Anthropic's Claude models. It is optimized for environmental and agricultural reports, transforming unstructured PDF content into structured JSON for downstream use.
